infinittt (0.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Qt6-based GUI with zoomable/pannable board
  * Command-line interface
  * Multiple AI opponents (Smart Random, Hybrid Evaluator, Hybrid Evaluator V2)
  * Configurable AI weight files
  * Automatic first move placement
  * Touch gesture support for Android compatibility

